rtw88: add h2c command in debugfs

It's very useful to send H2C command for debug usage. Add an entry
for sending H2C command to firmware.

usage example:
echo 42,00,00,43,02,00,00,00 > /sys/kernel/debug/ieee80211/phyX/rtw88

